<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Recordatorio de cita - Pet-Health</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#F0F4F8;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#F0F4F8;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:40px 20px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(27,42,74,0.08);">
          
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1B2A4A 0%,#2C3E6B 100%);padding:40px 40px 32px;text-align:center;">
              <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 64 64" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="display:block;margin:0 auto 16px auto;">
  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" fill="none" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.6"/>
  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="22" fill="#F59E0B" opacity="0.15"/>
  <g fill="#F59E0B">
    <ellipse cx="22" cy="38" rx="4" ry="5"/>
    <ellipse cx="32" cy="42" rx="4" ry="5"/>
    <ellipse cx="42" cy="38" rx="4" ry="5"/>
    <ellipse cx="18" cy="30" rx="3" ry="4"/>
    <ellipse cx="46" cy="30" rx="3" ry="4"/>
    <ellipse cx="32" cy="26" rx="8" ry="7"/>
  </g>
</svg>
              <h1 style="color:#ffffff;font-size:26px;margin:0;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;">PET-HEALTH</h1>
              <p style="color:#7ED7A8;font-size:12px;margin:8px 0 0 0;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;">Clínica Veterinaria</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Reminder Badge -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:40px 40px 0;">
              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#FFFBEB;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;border-left:4px solid #F59E0B;margin-bottom:24px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="width:40px;vertical-align:middle;">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width:32px;height:32px;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:50%;">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:18px;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold;line-height:32px;font-family:Georgia,serif;">i</td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                  <td style="vertical-align:middle;">
                    <p style="color:#92400E;font-size:14px;margin:0;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;">Recordatorio para mañana</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:0 40px 32px;">
              <h2 style="color:#1B2A4A;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Recordatorio de cita</h2>
              <div style="width:50px;height:4px;background:#F59E0B;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:28px;"></div>
              
              <p style="color:#4A5568;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 20px 0;">
                Hola <strong style="color:#1B2A4A;">{{nombrePropietario}}</strong>,
              </p>
              <p style="color:#4A5568;font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 28px 0;">
                Le recordamos que <strong style="color:#1B2A4A;">{{nombreMascota}}</strong> tiene una cita programada para <strong>mañana</strong>. No olvide asistir puntualmente.
              </p>
              
              <!-- Info Box -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#F8FAFC;border-radius:16px;padding:24px;margin-bottom:28px;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:16px 20px;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#718096;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:600;">Fecha</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#1B2A4A;font-size:16px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;">{{fecha}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;height:1px;padding:0;"></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#718096;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:600;">Hora</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#1B2A4A;font-size:16px;text-align:right;font-weight:700;">{{hora}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;height:1px;padding:0;"></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#718096;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:600;">Motivo</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#1B2A4A;font-size:16px;text-align:right;font-weight:500;">{{motivo}}</td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td colspan="2" style="border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;height:1px;padding:0;"></td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#718096;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:600;">Mascota</td>
                        <td style="padding:10px 0;color:#1B2A4A;font-size:16px;text-align:right;font-weight:500;">{{nombreMascota}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#EFF6FF;border-radius:12px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:32px;border-left:4px solid #3B82F6;">
                <tr>
                  <td>
                    <p style="color:#1E40AF;font-size:14px;margin:0;line-height:1.6;">
                      <strong>¿Necesita reprogramar?</strong> Contáctenos lo antes posible para encontrar una nueva fecha que se ajuste a su agenda.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <!-- CTA Buttons -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-bottom:8px;">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center" style="padding-bottom:12px;">
                    <a href="#" style="display:inline-block;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7ED7A8 0%,#5BC88A 100%);color:#1B2A4A;text-decoration:none;padding:16px 40px;border-radius:12px;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(126,215,168,0.3);">
                      Confirmar asistencia
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="#" style="display:inline-block;background:#ffffff;color:#1B2A4A;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 32px;border-radius:12px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;border:2px solid #E2E8F0;">
                      Reprogramar cita
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background:#F8FAFC;padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid #E2E8F0;text-align:center;">
              <p style="color:#1B2A4A;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin:0 0 4px 0;">Pet-Health Clínica Veterinaria</p>
              <p style="color:#718096;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 12px 0;">Cuidando a quienes más amas</p>
              <p style="color:#A0AEC0;font-size:12px;margin:0;">Este es un correo automático, por favor no responda directamente.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>